README.md

Technologies Used

HTML5

CSS3

Vanilla JavaScript

Intersection Observer animations

Pipedream for receiving form data

No backend server required

Fully static frontend compatible with any static hosting service

Deployment Notes

This project is meant to be deployed as a static site.

If using Render:

Select "Static Site"

Publish directory: ./https://university-landing-pages-xjnw.onrender.com/nigav2/frontend/uni1.html and https://university-landing-pages-xjnw.onrender.com/nigav2/frontend/uni2.html

Leave Build Command empty

No server is needed since the form posts directly to Pipedream

These landing pages can also be hosted on GitHub Pages, Netlify, or Vercel without any adjustments.
